TI  - The Influence of Negative Emotions on Mobile Phone Addiction Among Chinese College Students: The Mediating Role of Negative Coping Styles and the Moderating Role of Gender
T2  - PSYCHOLOGY RESEARCH AND BEHAVIOR MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
