TI  - How physical exercise influences academic burnout among Chinese "Double Non" college students: the chain mediation role of mobile phone addiction and learning engagement
T2  - FRONTIERS IN PSYCHOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - physical exercise
KW  - mobile phone addiction
KW  - learning engagement
KW  - academic burnout
KW  - "Double Non" college students
KW  - UNIVERSITY-STUDENTS
