TI  - The Impact of Perceived Discrimination on Mobile Phone Addiction Among Chinese Higher Vocational College Students: A Chain Mediating Role of Negative Emotions and Learning Burnout
T2  - PSYCHOLOGY RESEARCH AND BEHAVIOR MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - perceived discrimination
KW  - mobile phone addiction
KW  - negative emotions
KW  - learning burnout
KW  - structural equation model
