TI  - Prevalence and associated factors of migraine among female college students with premenstrual syndrome
T2  - SCIENTIFIC REPORTS
LA  - English
KW  - Premenstrual syndrome
KW  - Migraine
KW  - Female college students
KW  - Associated factors
KW  - DYSPHORIC DISORDER
